channel.title: Lylat - mstar (synth wave/electronic) + Announcement
channel.description:
Even though this track is 2 months old, I'd figure I should post this track on the disco.
[Soundcloud Link](https://soundcloud.com/user-474674955/lylat)
An interesting fact about this track, for some of the background percussion, I utilized some samples from the original Star Fox (SNES) game.
Also, I'm sorry for not really being active on here (life and school, oof). More music is in the works!
Cheers! - mstar
